Title: Empty Eyes

GuestStars: Mykel Shannon Jenkins, Matt Thompson, Tiffany DuPont, Walton Goggins, Marshall Allman, Ruby Dee, Sheeri Rappaport, Larry Mitchell, Charlie Weber, Kellan Lutz, Nadine Heimann, Betsy Rue, Robert Gant
